events.text:
Well, well, so you've made it to the top. [nw = v]
You've gambled your life just for it to end here. 
I am the one who locked you in this casino to punish your sins. 
As you are one of the most notorious gamblers this universe has seen, I can no longer allow you to continue. 
The truth is, me, my child and the holy spirit have been running all the world's casinos. 
You know it's quite expensive to keep heaven up and running so we need to make money somehow.
But now that you know this, I can not allow you to leave. 
Your journey ends now!
